[SPEAKER_00] Možete muži žena.

399
00:16:51,940 --> 00:16:53,940
[SPEAKER_00] Možeš sam ako nemaš kime.

400
00:16:53,940 --> 00:16:54,940
[SPEAKER_00] Uspiješ super.

401
00:16:54,940 --> 00:16:55,940
[SPEAKER_00] Malo naglas čitaj.

402
00:16:55,940 --> 00:16:57,940
[SPEAKER_00] Evo čitajmo ih kao ljubavno pismo.

403
00:16:57,940 --> 00:16:58,940
[SPEAKER_00] Sjetite se.

404
00:16:58,940 --> 00:17:00,940
[SPEAKER_00] Mi stari smo malo imali pisma.

405
