406
00:17:01,940 --> 00:17:02,940
[SPEAKER_00] Sad samo su poruke.

407
00:17:02,940 --> 00:17:05,940
[SPEAKER_00] Kako si čuvao pismo svoje zaručnice koja te ljubi ili zaručnika.

408
00:17:05,940 --> 00:17:09,940
[SPEAKER_00] Kako si to čuvao, mirisao i čitao svaku toliko.

409
00:17:09,940 --> 00:17:11,940
[SPEAKER_00] I da ponovo ti se zapali srce.

410
00:17:11,940 --> 00:17:12,940
[SPEAKER_00] Da te ona ljubi.

411
00:17:12,940 --> 00:17:14,940
[SPEAKER_00] Zato mi ovo ponovo čitamo.

412
00:17:14,940 --> 00:17:15,940
[SPEAKER_00] Da sve znamo na pamet.

413
00:17:15,940 --> 00:17:17,940
[SPEAKER_00] Opet i ponovo čitali u velikom tjednu.

414
00:17:17,940 --> 00:17:19,940
[SPEAKER_00] I izvan velikog tjedna.

415
00:17:19,940 --> 00:17:21,940
[SPEAKER_00] U velikom tjednu posebno nas to dira jače.

416
00:17:21,940 --> 00:17:22,940
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto?

417
