[SPEAKER_00] Evo da ponovo mi se zapali srce.

418
00:17:24,940 --> 00:17:25,940
[SPEAKER_00] Da ponovo briznem u plać.

419
00:17:25,940 --> 00:17:27,940
[SPEAKER_00] Da se ponovo vratim u ovoj ljubavi.

420
00:17:27,940 --> 00:17:29,940
[SPEAKER_00] Koja stoji posred pakla ovog svijeta.

421
00:17:29,940 --> 00:17:31,940
[SPEAKER_00] Posred kaosa ovog svijeta.

422
